{"tid":1533952,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"跨界別罷工集會坐滿添馬公園　警方稱高峰時3700人","createTime":"2019-09-03T00:57:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T07:11:39.000Z","uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"815a63bd4ebd77a1400c8047ad7f212584e09c6c","tid":1533952,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T00:57:36.000Z","msg":"跨界別罷工集會昨日下午在添馬公園舉行，參加者坐滿添馬公園。大會表示，集會有來自超過29個界別、超過4萬人參與。警方表示，高峰時有3700人。有集會籌備組的代表說，「九二九三全民罷工」行動今日繼續，又將9月13日設為死線，要求政府回應五大訴求。"},{"pid":"394444bf66736772ee77dc382ce2d6ed11a93289","tid":1533952,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:31:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6c046de016d89cbc496f70a26c7d89f63ffcfb8","tid":1533952,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:33:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />撐警?"},{"pid":"e38663f23c1b1c3470d81b65aeec913720747b92","tid":1533952,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6c046de016d89cbc496f70a26c7d89f63ffcfb8","tid":1533952,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:33:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />撐警?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:50:16.000Z","msg":"47萬，狗話10萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1804e2923ce463b55be9fb82a5ae062a6909eb77","tid":1533952,"uid":65790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:50:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26c0eaa4e016baf8910bc7388bdc1ee3f414e32e","tid":1533952,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:53:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"522e590d3a0f758cf636495a82f1f5ab28853515","tid":1533952,"uid":30604,"like":0